to download ansible
enable epel using 
yum install https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
 
yum install update

yum install ansible

to install apche we will use command 
ansible localhoast -m yum -a "name=httpd state=present"
to start apache
ansible localhoast -m service -a "name=httpd state=started"
